        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>GridBankApi</h2>
        <p>GridBankApi is a WebApi RESTful service used by CentralHub to collect usage data from the remote GridBank.  It is also used by GridBank to store all usage information in a SQL Server database.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>GridBank</h2>
